ping_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Ping\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**:  AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n`.ping`\n\nThe ping command in Ciraag is a tool used to measure the response time of the userbot to a given message. It essentially sends a test message and measures how long it takes the userbot to respond. This can be helpful for diagnosing issues with the userbot's responsiveness or for simply checking its status."

self_destruct_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Self Destruct\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**: AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n**Reply to timer media**: `.tmd`\n\nSelf-destruct media in Telegram is a feature that allows you to send photos and videos that automatically disappear after a certain amount of time. Once the timer expires, the media cannot be viewed or recovered. This feature is designed to provide an extra layer of privacy and security for sensitive information."

raid_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Reply Raid\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**: AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n**To add to enemy list**: Use the `.so` command to reply to the enemy's message.\n**To delete from enemy list**: To remove an enemy from the list, use the `.ro` command in the enemy's message reply.\n\nReply Raid is a term used to describe a malicious or spammy activity in the context of Telegram userbots where a bot automatically replies to every message in a chat, often with the same or similar message. It is created only to respond to the enemy side."

bomb_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Slang Bombs\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**: AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n.bomb [amount]\n\n**.bomb**: This is the command to trigger the bomb function.\n\n**[amount]**: This is an optional numerical argument that specifies the amount of the bomb. The exact meaning of amount will depend on the specific implementation of the bomb function.\n\nSlang bombing is a type of spam attack that involves sending unsolicited, often offensive or inappropriate, messages to a targeted individual. These attacks can quickly overwhelm a user's inbox, making it difficult to use the platform. Beyond being a nuisance, spam text attacks can also be used to distribute malware, which can potentially harm a device or steal personal information."

gemini_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Gemini\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**: AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n`.gemini Who are you?`\n\nGemini is a large language model chatbot developed by Google AI.  It excels at generating text, translating languages, writing different kinds of creative content, and answering your questions in an informative way, even if they are open ended, challenging, or strange.  Essentially, it's a highly advanced conversational AI designed for a wide range of tasks."

spam_usage = "**Plugin Name**: Bomb\n**Developer**: iniridwanul\n**License**: AGPL-3.0\n\nUsage:\n`.cbomb [amount] [message]`\n\nMessage spamming involves sending excessive and often unwanted messages containing slang terms or informal language. This can be disruptive, annoying, and sometimes even offensive to recipients."